Key Match Events: Niclas Fuellkrug headed in an 85th minute goal to give Germany a 2-1 comeback victory over Netherlands.
Joey Veerman scored in the 4th minute for Netherlands.
Maximilian Mittelstädt scored in the 11th minute for Germany.
Wout Weghorst's left footed shot from the right side of the box was saved in the 90'+3' minute.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Germany achieved two victories from two matches in the past four days.
The match was held at Deutsche Bank Park in Frankfurt, Germany with an attendance of 48,390.
